title: Index of Factory Payrolls, Machinery for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1919-1942 (2)--Original Data, 1947-1954. Data Does Not Include Transportation Equipment. Source: Bureau Of Labor Statistics, 1919-1934 Data Are From A Bls Mimeographed Release, September 1938; 1935-1939 Data Are From A Bls Mimeographed Release, May 1940; 1940-1942 Data Are From "Employment And Payrolls" And Monthly Labor Review.

This NBER data series m08076a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 8 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter08.html.
